data.description: This move in ready walkout rambler is located in a fantastic Ramsey location just south of Rum River Hills Golf Club and is situated on a wooded 2.5 Acre lot! Features include an oversized attached garage plus an additional 2 car detached garage! House features a new roof, new flooring and paint throughout much of the home, granite counters in kitchen, spacious finished lower level with large family room, bathroom, wood stove, and potential 3rd bedroom (just needs an egress window installed), and much more! There will also be a new septic system installed! Natural gas is at the street for connection. This property is a great value and is priced to sell quickly, so get your showing scheduled today!
